IfcPropertySingleValue.NominalValue: Chicago Faucets No. 802-VXKABCP, polished chrome plated solid cast brass body construction with integral 4" C-C spout and integral inlet shanks on 4" centers. ECAST® construction with less than 0.25% lead content by weighted average. 2.2 GPM pressure compensating vandal resistant aerator outlet. 2-1/2" curved metal lever handles with eight point tapered broach and secured color coded index buttons with vandal resistant screws. Quarter-turn ceramic disc cartridge with square tapered broach feature to help facilitate handle removal. IfcPropertySingleValue.Name: Specification
IfcPropertySingleValue.NominalValue: Chicago Faucets No. 786-E3ABCP, polished chrome plated solid brass body and spout. ECAST® construction with less than 0.25% lead content by weighted average. 5-1/4" C-C rigid/swing field convertible gooseneck spout. 2.2 GPM pressure compensating aerator outlet. 4" wristblade handles with eight-point tapered broach and secured, color-coded index buttons.
